Welcome to RoboVasion, a free realtime stratagy game for GNU/Linux,
covered under the GPL. RoboVasion makes use of the Stratagus engine,
which is available at: 

 * http://www.nongnu.org/stratagus/

If you look for detailed installation instruction have a look at the
file INSTALL. For more infos, updates, new missions and other stuff on
RoboVasion itself you can visit the RoboVasion webpage at:

 * http://www.nongnu.org/robovasion/

'Sourcecode' (in the form of multilayer .xcf files) for most of the
graphics that are used in RoboVasion is inside the CVS repository,
which can be accessed with:

 $ cvs -d:pserver:anoncvs@subversions.gnu.org:/cvsroot/robovasion login
 $ cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anoncvs@subversions.gnu.org:/cvsroot/robovasion co robovasion

Questions, comments, bug reports and other stuff you want the
RoboVasion development team to know can be send to the:

 * RoboVasion Development List <robovasion-devel@nongnu.org>

